 'channel' will echo current channel value; 
'channel N' will set N(assuming valid) as current channel.

@jph00 
1) all the models that use the load_pre loader (e.g. inception4, inceptionresnet_2, resnext50, resnext101, resnext101_64, wrn) will fail without pre-creating the weights directory, we can add that logic to load_pre to unify things if you would like.

2)if you like this method of passing the url can add that logic to the existing classes.  inceptionresnet_2 has a similar model structure inception4 but the other models (eg. resnext variants + wrn) will need to be customized slightly.  the torchvision models use the torch loader directly.
